play USB computer headset, you won't need to worry about any complicated set up processes or software downloads.\nThe padded comfort of the H390 is also worth mentioning. With swivel-mounted, leatherette ear cushions that are easy to clean, you can be sure that these headphones will provide hours of comfortable wear. And with a 6.23 ft (1.9 m) USB A cable that's just the right length, you can move freely during long conversations or video calls.\nFinally, the H390 is also a sustainable choice. With 23%* of the plastic parts in the headset made from post-consumer recycled plastic, and responsible packaging that uses FSC-certified paper, you can feel good about your purchase knowing that it's helping to protect the environment.\nOverall, the Logitech H390 is an excellent choice for anyone looking for a reliable and affordable wired headset for their PC or laptop. With its digital stereo sound, noise canceling microphone, in-line controls, and comfortable design, it's a headset that's sure to meet all your audio needs.", ":\n## JBL Quantum 100 - Wired Over-Ear Gaming Headphones - Black, Large \n### Reasons to buy\nIf you're a gamer or a casual listener looking for a high-quality set of headphones, the JBL Quantum 100 is definitely worth considering. The over-ear design provides a comfortable fit, even during extended gaming sessions. The headphones are also equipped with a high-quality sound driver that delivers a crisp and clear audio experience. \n### Key Features\n- Over-ear design for optimal sound isolation and comfort\n- High-quality sound driver for crystal-clear audio\n- Comfortable fit for extended gaming sessions\n- In-line microphone and controller for convenient voice and game audio management\n- Detachable cables for easy replacement and durability\n### Conclusion\nIf you're in the market for a new set of gaming headphones, the JBL Quantum 100 is definitely worth considering. The over-ear design provides a comfortable fit, while the high-quality sound driv